<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Portfolio</title>

  <!-- Google Font -->
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Pretendard:wght@300;400;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">

  <style>
    :root {
      --bg: #0f172a;
      --card: #111827;
      --primary: #6366f1;
      --text: #e5e7eb;
      --sub: #9ca3af;
    }

    * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }

    body {
      font-family: 'Pretendard', sans-serif;
      background: var(--bg);
      color: var(--text);
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    header {
      position: sticky;
      top: 0;
      background: rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.8);
      backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
      border-bottom: 1px solid #1f2937;
      z-index: 100;
    }

    nav {
      max-width: 1100px;
      margin: auto;
      padding: 20px;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
    }

    nav h1 { font-size: 18px; }

    nav ul {
      list-style: none;
      display: flex;
      gap: 20px;
    }

    nav a {
      text-decoration: none;
      color: var(--sub);
      transition: 0.3s;
    }

    nav a:hover { color: var(--text); }

    section {
      max-width: 1100px;
      margin: auto;
      padding: 80px 20px;
    }

    .hero {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 140px 20px 100px;
    }

    .hero h2 {
      font-size: 36px;
      font-weight: 700;
      margin-bottom: 15px;
    }

    .hero p {
      color: var(--sub);
      font-size: 18px;
    }

    .btn {
      display: inline-block;
      margin-top: 30px;
      padding: 12px 24px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: var(--primary);
      color: white;
      text-decoration: none;
      transition: 0.3s;
    }

    .btn:hover { opacity: 0.8; }

    h2.section-title {
      font-size: 24px;
      margin-bottom: 30px;
    }

    .projects {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(260px, 1fr));
      gap: 25px;
    }

    .card {
      background: var(--card);
      padding: 25px;
      border-radius: 16px;
      border: 1px solid #1f2937;
      transition: 0.3s;
    }

    .card:hover {
      transform: translateY(-6px);
      border-color: var(--primary);
    }

    .card h3 {
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }

    .card p {
      color: var(--sub);
      font-size: 14px;
    }

    footer {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 40px 20px;
      border-top: 1px solid #1f2937;
      color: var(--sub);
    }

    @media (max-width: 600px) {
      .hero h2 { font-size: 26px; }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

<header>
  <nav>
    <h1>Namwook</h1>
    <ul>
      <li><a href="#about">About</a></li>
      <li><a href="#projects">Projects</a></li>
      <li><a href="#contact">Contact</a></li>
    </ul>
  </nav>
</header>

<section class="hero">
  <h2>Computer Vision Engineer</h2>
  <p>영상처리 · 검사 알고리즘 · 반도체 검사 장비 개발</p>
  <a href="#projects" class="btn">프로젝트 보기</a>
</section>

<section id="about">
  <h2 class="section-title">About</h2>
  <p>
    15년 이상의 경력을 가진 영상처리 개발자로,
    반도체 및 2차전지 검사 장비의 알고리즘 개발과 최적화를 수행하고 있습니다.
  </p>
</section>

<section id="projects">
  <h2 class="section-title">Projects</h2>

  <div class="projects">

    <div class="card">
      <h3>Defect Detection System</h3>
      <p>Sub-pixel alignment 기반 고정밀 결함 검출 알고리즘 개발</p>
    </div>

    <div class="card">
      <h3>Optical Inspection Optimization</h3>
      <p>조명 및 카메라 조건 최적화로 검출력 향상</p>
    </div>

    <div class="card">
      <h3>AI Inspection Module</h3>
      <p>딥러닝 기반 검사 시스템 적용 및 성능 개선</p>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>

<section id="contact">
  <h2 class="section-title">Contact</h2>
  <p>Email: your@email.com</p>
  <p>GitHub: github.com/yourname</p>
</section>

<footer>
  <p>© 2026 Namwook Portfolio</p>
</footer>

</body>
</html>
